'''''Champions''''' ({{lang-es|'''Campeones'''}}) is a 2018 Spanish [[comedy-drama]] film directed by [[Javier Fesser]].<ref name="El Español">{{cite web|url=https://www.elespanol.com/cultura/cine/20180405/campeones-ensenaron-fesser-no-dice-subnormales/297470779_0.html |title=Los campeones que enseñaron a Fesser que no se dice “subnormales” |last=Zurro|first=Javier|work=''El Español'' |date=5 April 2018|accessdate=14 August 2018}}</ref><ref name="eldiario.es">{{cite web|url=https://www.eldiario.es/cultura/Fesser-atribuye-Campeones-felices-espectadores_0_767474160.html|title=Fesser atribuye el éxito de "Campeones" a que "hace felices" a los espectadores |work=[[EFE]]|publisher=''[[eldiario.es]]'' |date=3 May 2018|accessdate=14 August 2018}}</ref> It was selected as the Spanish entry for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]] at the [[91st Academy Awards]].<ref name="91stOscars">{{cite tweet |author=Academia de Cine|user=Academiadecine |number=1037635456664518657|date=6 September 2018|title=El actor @DanielGrao7 anuncia en la Academia que Campeones, de Javier Fesser es la película que representará a España en la 91 edición de los Oscar en la categoría de Mejor Película de Habla No Inglesa|language=es}}</ref><ref name="Spain2">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/festivals/javier-fessers-champions-spain-oscar-submission-1202929366/ |title=Javier Fesser’s ‘Champions’ Chosen as Spain’s Oscar Submission |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |first=John |last=Hopewell |date=6 September 2018 |accessdate=6 September 2018}}</ref>
==Plot== Marco Montes is the assistant coach of the basketball team [[CB Estudiantes]]. He is an arrogant man with bad manners, He is fired from his job after an altercation with his head coach during a game. After driving drunk into the back of a police car, Marco is ordered to do community service, in the form of coaching Los Amigos, a team of guys with disabilities.<ref name="HollywoodReporter">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/champions-review-1104765|title=‘Champions’ (‘Campeones’): Film Review|last=Holland|first=Jonathan|publisher=''[[The Hollywood Reporter]]'' |date=23 April 2018|accessdate=14 August 2018}}</ref>
