{{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}}
The '''DB Draught Classic''' was a major [[thoroughbred]] horse race in [[New Zealand]]. Run at Ellerslie and New Zealand's first million-dollar race, it was run only twice in 1989 and 1990. Both editions were won by Japan Cup winner Horlicks.

