{{Infobox gymnast |name= Susanna Marchesi |gender= w |image= |image_size= |caption= |fullname= |altname= |nickname= |country= {{flagu|Italy}} |regions= |formercountry= |birth_date= {{birth date and age|1980|3|13|df=y}} |birth_place= |hometown= |residence= |death_date= |death_place= |height= |discipline= RG |level= Senior International Elite |natlteam= 1999-2004 (?) |club= |gym= |collegeteam= |headcoach= |assistcoach= |formercoach= |choreographer= |music= |eponymousskills= |retired= |worldranking= |updated= |show-medals= yes |medaltemplates= <!-- see [[Template:MedalRelatedTemplates]] --> }} '''Susanna Marchesi''' (born 13 March 1980) is a former Italian individual [[rhythmic gymnast]]. She represents her nation at international competitions.
