'''TOBB Sport Hall''' ({{lang-tr|TOBB Spor Salonu}}) is an indoor multi-purpose sport venue that is located in the [[TOBB University of Economics and Technology|TOBB University of Economics and Technology Söğütözü Campus]], [[Ankara]], [[Turkey]]. The hall, with a capacity for 2,000 spectators, was built in 2007.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.biletix.com/mekan/OK/ANKARA/tr |publisher=biletix.com |title=TOBB Spor Salonu |language=Turkish |accessdate=2015-01-03 }}</ref> It is home to [[TED Ankara Kolejliler]], which plays currently in the [[Turkish Basketball League]].


