{{Infobox National Olympic Committee | title = Uganda Olympic Committee | logo = | size = | country = Uganda | code = UGA | created = 1950 | recognized = 1956 | association = ANOCA | headquarters = [[Kampala]] | president = William Frederick Blick | secretary general = Dr. Donald Rukare | website = [http://www.nocuganda.org/ Uganda Olympic Committee] | notes = }} The '''Uganda Olympic Committee''' (IOC code: '''UGA''') is the [[National Olympic Committee]] representing [[Uganda]]. It was created in 1950 and officially recognised by the [[International Olympic Committee]] in 1956.<ref name=uoc/>
